: \"frontend服务出现大量\\\"could not retrieve cart: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\\\"和\\\"rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = timed out waiting for server handshake\\\"错误，同时cartservice出现\\\"System.IO.IOException: The client reset the request stream\\\"和\\\"Error reading message\\\"错误\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"server_error_ratio\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Multiple frontend pods (frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2) showed significant spikes in error_ratio and server_error_ratio, with values reaching up to 30.19. Additionally, rrt and rrt_max metrics for frontend-2 showed extreme values, indicating potential performance degradation.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio for frontend-2 increased from 0.0 to 30.19, rrt for frontend-2 increased from 12140.95 to 13435422.36.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"shippingservice-1 showed a spike in client_error_ratio (from 0.0 to 62.75) and error_ratio (from 0.0 to 62.75), indicating potential issues with service reliability.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio for shippingservice-1 increased from 0.0 to 62.75.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"cartservice-2 showed a spike in error_ratio (from 0.0 to 47.76) and client_error_ratio (from 0.0 to 47.76), suggesting potential issues with the service.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio for cartservice-2 increased from 0.0 to 47.76.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"productcatalogservice-0 showed a spike in client_error_ratio (from 0.0 to 58.7), indicating potential issues with the service.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio for productcatalogservice-0 increased from 0.0 to 58.7.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\n基于Trace数据的分析，我已经识别出了异常事件的根本原因。以下是详细分析：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"frontend->cartservice\", \"cartservice->redis\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService相关操作延迟异常激增：GetCart操作从正常2.5-39秒激增至5900万秒（约164小时），AddItem操作从5.2秒激增至6000万秒\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"Redis HGET操作从正常1.5秒激增至4.9万秒，表明cartservice依赖的Redis存储出现严重性能问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端服务出现大量500错误（HTTP status code: 500）和context canceled错误，是cartservice延迟导致的连锁反应\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 根因分析总结\n\n**根本原因**: Redis存储层性能严重下降，导致cartservice服务无法正常访问购物车数据，进而引发整个调用链的级联故障。\n\n**故障传播路径**:\n1. **根因层**: Redis存储性能异常（HGET操作延迟增加3000倍）\n2. **直接影响层**: cartservice服务因Redis访问超时而出现严重延迟\n3. **连锁反应层**: frontend服务调用cartservice时超时，产生大量500错误和context canceled\n4. **用户影响**: 前端页面无法正常加载购物车和添加商品功能\n\n**关键证据**:\n- cartservice的GetCart/AddItem操作延迟增加超过1000倍\n- Redis HGET操作延迟异常激增\n- 大量context canceled和transport closing错误表明连接超时\n- 前端服务出现大量500错误响应\n\n建议优先检查Redis集群的健康状态和网络连接，然后检查cartservice与Redis之间的连接配置。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "Redis存储层性能严重下降是根本原因，导致cartservice服务无法正常访问购物车数据，进而引发整个调用链的级联故障"}
